title: RHOC: Neckless Endangerment
description:
We're closing out the 16th season of Real Housewives of Orange County with one last installment of the reunion. This time we're discussing Shannon's neck, Cards Against Humanity, and Dr. Jen's fascinating home life.

Be sure to watch our recap with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/65719814
